steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit015" and Comment "Testing for checking empty and duplicate index"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit015" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol015" Type "integer" for Table name "jit015"
When I open add-index popup of table "jit015"
When I input index data: list column "id" - unique "true" - name "default" for Index number "1"
When I press Add index button of modal popup
When I input index data: list column "jitcol015" - unique "true" - name "default" for Index number "2"
When I press Save button modal popup
When I open add-index popup of table "jit015"
Then I should see dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "1" has value "id"
Then I should see checkbox Unique of Index number "1" has value "true"
Then I should see textbox Index name of Index number "1" with value "index_jit015s_on_id"
Then I should see dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "2" has value "jitcol015"
Then I should see checkbox Unique of Index number "2" has value "true"
Then I should see textbox Index name of Index number "2" with value "index_jit015s_on_jitcol015"
When I update dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "1" with value "created_at"
When I add dropdown Index column index "2" of Index number "1" with value "id"
When I select checkbox Unique of Index number "1" with value "false"
When I input textbox Index name of Index number "1" with value "jitera_index"
When I press Save button modal popup
When I open add-index popup of table "jit015"
Then I should see dropdown Index column index "1" of Index number "1" has value "created_at"
